00001| """
00002| Helper functions for interpreting literal values and manipulating object graph
00003| state during analysis. These utilities sit between the AST handlers and the
00004| Graph class, providing small conversions (e.g., JS literal evaluation,
00005| wildcard handling) and branch-aware copy helpers.
